Package: vlightr
Type: Package
Title: Persistent Conditional Formatting for Vectors
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ethan Sansom
Maintainer: ethan.sansom29@gmail.com
Description: Provides a vector superclass with persistant conditional formatting. 
    `highlight` an arbitrary vector to color, emphasize, or otherwise reformat 
    elements of interest when printed for easier EDA and bug catching.
